<P align=right>Page 65</P></font><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY"> (including sex) were hurt or threatened.  So we were sore.  We were &quot;burned up.&quot;</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">On our grudge list we set opposite each name our  injuries.  Was it our self-esteem, our security, our ambitions, our personal, or sex relations, which had been  interfered with?</P>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">We were usually as definite as this example:</P><PRE>
